					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yeah, 120 Hz and below is low enough frequency you're going to have difficulty seeing it in a spectrogram. Just look at the direct waveform, and count the number of milliseconds between zero-crossings (4 or 8) or repetitions (8 or 16).</div>

